git status
git log
git show commit_id
git remote add origin url
git push -u origin master

TO CREATE A BRANCH, MERGE & STASH:

git branch = list available branches
git branch branch_name = create a new branch
git checkout branch_name_you_want_to_go = to switch branch
git branch -d branch_name = to delete branch
git log --oneline = to list branch in oneline

MERGE:

git merge branch_name = to merge branches
git log = to verify merge
git push origin master = to push to central repo like github

STASHING:

git stash = to stash an item
git stash list = to see stashed item list
git stash apply stash@{0} = to apply stashed item
git stash clear = to clear stash item

GIT RESET:

git reset filename = reset staging area file
git reset =  reset staging area
git reset --hard = to reset changes from both staging area and working directory at a time.

REVERT:

git revert commit_id = undo an existing commit
